- PHP 7.4 (Silex, Kohana, Laravel, Symfony);
- Шаблонизатор Twig;
- Python;
- NoSQL: Redis, Memcached;
- PostgreSQL, MSSQL;
- CI/CD;
- Docker/Kubernetes;
- GitLab/Kibana;
